@startuml
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam note {
    BackgroundColor #F7FCFF
    BorderColor #88BBDD
    FontSize 12
}

note over App, VFS
打开硬链接核心要点
1.硬链接dentry直接指向原文件inode，无类型特殊标记
2.i_nlink只是计数，打开流程和普通文件完全一致
3.不会路径跳转，fd直接绑定原inode
end note

box "【用户态 User Space】" #LightYellow
actor App
end box

box "【内核态 Kernel Space】" #LightCyan
participant "VFS 虚拟文件系统" as VFS
participant "硬链接dentry" as HardDentry
participant "原文件inode" as RealInode
participant "file结构体" as File
end box
database Disk

App -> VFS: <color:red>①</color> open("/b/hardlink", O_RDONLY)
activate VFS

VFS -> HardDentry: <color:red>②</color> 路径查找拿到硬链接dentry
activate HardDentry
HardDentry --> VFS: <color:red>③</color> dentry绑定原文件ino，直接返回原inode
note right: 硬链接无S_IFLNK标记，内核识别为普通文件
deactivate HardDentry

VFS -> RealInode: <color:red>④</color> 权限、文件属性校验
activate RealInode
RealInode --> VFS: 校验通过
deactivate RealInode

VFS -> File: <color:red>⑤</color> 分配struct file，绑定原inode
activate File
File --> VFS
deactivate File

VFS -> VFS: <color:red>⑥</color> 分配fd
VFS --> App: <color:red>⑦</color> 返回fd，fd指向源文件inode
deactivate VFS
@enduml